author: Deidre Davison
text: The best ways to heal & move fwd. Let loved ones in as communication is key. The answers u seek r coming.  Conclusions r w/in reach. Emotions r running high so find balance. Ur hard work is paying off. Make the 1st move w/ boldness & confidence.

author: Deidre Davison
text: A win/win in a new start is coming. Look @ the big picture knowing ur good enuff. Don't let pride get in ur way during this time of healing. This is the time 2 give urself ❤️ grace, mercy & 4giveness. Move fwd w/ confidence as prosperity lies ahead.  Meditate & contemplate (Cont)

author: Deidre Davison
text: People will expect you to fully see, hear, love & support them but will absolutely choose not to do the same for you. Make sure you show up for & give yourself all of these things without absorbing their negative energy.

author: Deidre Davison
text: Divine Feminines, remember when you were w/ your Divine Masculine & you were able to be so open & vulnerable w/ him? More vulnerable than you could be w/ yourself? Give yourself that same space to be that open & vulnerable w/ yourself.

author: Deidre Davison
text: Sometimes the way we cry for help is by crying about how much worse we have it than someone else. Until we learn nobody can heal us but ourselves,  we will continue to expect it to come from someone else. https://t.co/MkpUNm8Hdg
